                                 Sizing: the PNG is cropped to the bare controller silhouette (96x66, no
                                 padding) and the Viewbox is 20x18 rather than 18x18. A controller is much
                                 wider than tall, so a square 18x18 Viewbox caps it on WIDTH and leaves the
